snippet.title: Fussball #24 - VC 4000
snippet.description: This little football game plays like the classic Stiga hockey or football games, with metal rods to controll each player horisontally. This is a very good controller layout, and recreates the same fun as we had on the Stiga games. Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/07/fussball-24-vc-4000.html
